      'Limited testing options',
      'Basic monitoring',
    ],
    bestFor: [
      { label: 'Best for Convenience', variant: 'primary', icon: 'zap' },
    ],
  },
];

// Quick picks for this category
const quickPicks = [
  {
    segment: 'budget' as const,
    brandName: 'Hims',
    brandSlug: 'hims',
    detail: '$79/month, no consult fee',
  },
  {
    segment: 'privacy' as const,
    brandName: 'Hone Health',
    brandSlug: 'hone-health',
    detail: 'Discreet, comprehensive testing',
  },
  {
    segment: 'speed' as const,
    brandName: 'Hims',
    brandSlug: 'hims',
    detail: 'Quick approval, fast shipping',
  },
  {
    segment: 'quality' as const,
    brandName: 'Hone Health',
    brandSlug: 'hone-health',
    detail: 'Expert MDs, full hormone panel',
  },
];

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'MedicalWebPage',
  name: 'Best TRT Clinics & Testosterone Therapy Services',
  description: 'Compare the best online testosterone replacement therapy (TRT) clinics and hormone optimization services.',
  about: {
    '@type': 'MedicalCondition',
    name: 'Low Testosterone',
  },
};

// FAQ data for AI-SEO optimization
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How much does TRT cost through online clinics?",
    answer: "Online TRT costs $150-300 per month for medication plus $100-250 for initial consultation and lab work. Hone Health charges $199 consultation + $150-250/month for treatment. Vault Health costs $250 setup + $200-300/month. TRT Nation has $250 consultation but lower medication costs at $99-150/month. Most clinics require quarterly lab work ($100-200) for monitoring."
  },
  {
    question: "Do I need a testosterone test before starting TRT?",
    answer: "Yes, you must have blood test results showing low testosterone before starting TRT. Normal testosterone levels are 300-1000 ng/dL. Most online clinics require levels below 350 ng/dL (some below 300 ng/dL) to prescribe TRT. You'll need two morning tests taken before 10 AM to confirm diagnosis. All reputable TRT clinics require lab work - avoid services that don't test first."
  },
  {
    question: "Is online TRT legal and safe?",
    answer: "Yes, online TRT is completely legal when prescribed by licensed physicians following proper protocols. Services like Hone Health, Vault Health, and Maximus use board-certified doctors who review lab results before prescribing. They require regular blood work (every 3-6 months) to monitor safety. Online TRT follows the same medical standards as in-person clinics - the only difference is convenience of virtual consultations."
  },
  {
    question: "What are the side effects of TRT?",
    answer: "Common TRT side effects include elevated red blood cell count (requires monitoring), acne or oily skin, testicular shrinkage, and reduced fertility. Less common side effects are mood changes, sleep apnea worsening, and gynecomastia (breast tissue growth from estrogen conversion). Most side effects are manageable through dosage adjustment or ancillary medications. Proper medical monitoring every 3-6 months minimizes risks."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does TRT take to work?",
    answer: "TRT effects appear in stages. Energy and mood improve within 2-4 weeks. Libido and sexual function improve within 4-6 weeks. Muscle gain and fat loss become noticeable at 3-6 months. Full benefits (maximum muscle mass, optimal energy, best mood) take 6-12 months. Results vary by individual, baseline levels, and dosage. Injectable testosterone works faster than creams or gels."
  },
  {
    question: "What's the difference between testosterone injections vs creams?",
    answer: "Testosterone injections are administered weekly or bi-weekly with more stable blood levels and lower cost ($99-150/month). Testosterone creams/gels are applied daily, more convenient but cost more ($150-250/month) and have less consistent absorption. Injections are 85-90% effective at raising levels. Creams are 70-80% effective due to variable absorption. Most users prefer injections for effectiveness and value."
  },
  {
    question: "Will TRT affect my fertility?",
    answer: "Yes, TRT suppresses natural testosterone production and sperm production in 90% of men. Most men become infertile within 3-6 months of starting TRT. If fertility is a concern, consider alternatives like enclomiphene or HCG that preserve fertility while raising testosterone. Services like Maximus specialize in fertility-preserving options. Fertility usually returns 6-12 months after stopping TRT, but recovery isn't guaranteed."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I get TRT covered by insurance?",
    answer: "Most online TRT services don't accept insurance and operate on cash-pay basis. However, some like Vault Health provide documentation you can submit to insurance for potential reimbursement. Traditional insurance coverage for TRT is limited - many plans consider it optional or lifestyle treatment. Cash-pay online TRT ($150-300/month) is often comparable to insurance co-pays after deductibles anyway."
  },
  {
    question: "Which online TRT clinic is best?",
    answer: "Hone Health is best for comprehensive care with thorough testing and physician support ($199 consultation + $150-250/month). Maximus is best for fertility preservation with enclomiphene options ($149 consultation + $199/month all-inclusive). TRT Nation offers best value medication at $99-150/month but higher upfront costs ($250 consultation). Your choice depends on priorities: comprehensive care (Hone), fertility (Maximus), or affordability (TRT Nation)."
  },
  {
    question: "Do I have to stay on TRT forever?",
    answer: "Most men stay on TRT long-term (years or lifetime) because stopping causes testosterone to return to pre-treatment low levels within 3-6 months. Natural production may recover partially, but rarely returns to optimal levels, especially in older men. Some men cycle off TRT with PCT (post-cycle therapy) using HCG and clomiphene to restart natural production. Discuss long-term plans with your physician before starting."
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Best TRT Clinics - Compare Testosterone Therapy Services"
  description="Compare top testosterone replacement therapy (TRT) clinics and hormone optimization services. Find the best pricing, testing, and treatment options online."
  schema={schema}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-12 lg:py-16 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-6">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors">Home</a>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-slate-900 font-medium">Testosterone & Hormones</span>

        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-700 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          New to telehealth? We'll walk you through it
        </div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-tight px-4">
          TRT Clinics & Testosterone Therapy Compared
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 sm:mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
          Compare testosterone replacement therapy (TRT) clinics offering comprehensive hormone optimization, testing, and treatment plans.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="#comparison" class="btn-primary">
            View Comparison
          </a>
          <a href="#treatment-options" class="btn-outline">
            Treatment Options
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Stats -->
  <section class="py-10 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">7+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">TRT Services</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">$79+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Per Month</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">3-7</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Days to Start</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">95%+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Patient Satisfaction</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Picks Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <QuickPicks picks={quickPicks} category="Testosterone & Hormones" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Signals -->
  <section class="py-6 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <TrustSignals
        lastUpdated={new Date()}
        reviewsCount={8000}
        servicesCompared={7}
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Understanding Low Testosterone</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Low testosterone (hypogonadism) affects millions of men, causing fatigue, decreased libido, muscle loss,
          mood changes, and reduced quality of life. Modern TRT clinics offer convenient online consultations,
          comprehensive testing, and personalized treatment plans delivered to your door.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          The best TRT clinics provide regular monitoring, physician oversight, and multiple treatment options
          including injectable testosterone, testosterone creams, and alternative therapies like enclomiphene
          that preserve fertility.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison Section -->
  <section id="comparison" class="section-light">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3 px-4">
          TRT Clinic Comparison
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600">
          Updated {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', year: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
      </div>

      <ComparisonTable brands={brands} location="testosterone-table" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Treatment Options -->
  <section id="treatment-options" class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-center px-4">
        Treatment Options
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Compare the most common testosterone replacement therapy options.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card p-6 ring-2 ring-brand-accent">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="injection" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Injectable Testosterone</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Cypionate or Enanthate</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Most popular and cost-effective option. Injected 1-2 times weekly for stable testosterone levels.
            Available through most TRT clinics.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Pricing Range:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>• $99-250/month medication</li>
              <li>• $0-250 consultation</li>
              <li>• $50-199 lab testing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="lotion" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Testosterone Cream</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Topical Application</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Daily application cream absorbed through skin. No needles required. Good for those who prefer
            non-injectable options, though generally more expensive.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Pricing Range:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>• $150-300/month medication</li>
              <li>• Similar testing costs</li>
              <li>• Daily application required</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="pill" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Enclomiphene</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Alternative Therapy</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Oral medication that stimulates natural testosterone production. Preserves fertility unlike traditional
            TRT. Good option for younger men or those planning children.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Pricing Range:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>• $150-250/month medication</li>
              <li>• Maximus: $199/month all-in</li>
              <li>• Maintains fertility</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section with Schema Markup -->
  <section id="faq" class="section-light">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <FAQSection
        title="Common Questions About TRT & Testosterone Therapy"
        categoryName="Testosterone Replacement Therapy"
        faqs={faqs}
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Content -->
  <section class="section bg-white border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 text-center">
        Explore More Categories
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/sexual-health" class="card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="mb-3 flex justify-center">
            <Icon name="sexual-health" class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors">
            Sexual Health
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            ED treatments and sexual wellness solutions.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/weight-loss" class="card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="mb-3 flex justify-center">
            <Icon name="weight-loss" class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors">
            Weight Loss
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            GLP-1 medications and weight management programs.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/mental-health" class="card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="mb-3 flex justify-center">
            <Icon name="mental-health" class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors">
            Mental Health
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Online therapy and psychiatric care platforms.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
